App is used for showing multiple things in android

1.Fetch data from API http://www.androidbegin.com/tutorial/jsonparsetutorial.txt .
2.Displays the Images fetched using Picasso Library.
3.Dislays the details along with Images in a recycler view.
4.Clicking on an Image takes to an activity where the image sis shown enlarged
5.On pressing back button multple image view is restored.


The video is demo is available at https://drive.google.com/open?id=1fmABP6-2thN1JvOe3-2dMQ50-2OdGtxu
